        Encapsulates the various compression tables that Inbound Compression uses.

        Parameters:
        oldTables - is guaranteed to always have at-least one and at-most keepOldTables elements. It starts with containing only a single "disabled" table (versioned as DecompressionTable.DisabledVersion), and from there on continiously accumulates at most keepOldTables recently used tables.
